cff-version: 1.2.0
title: peoplereadmes
message: >-
  Please cite this work when using or adapting the persona context system
  or any of its persona packages.
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Koylan
    given-names: Muratcan
repository-code: https://github.com/muratcankoylan/peoplereadmes
url: https://github.com/muratcankoylan/peoplereadmes
abstract: >-
  Open-source framework for structured, evidence-bound, non-impersonating
  persona context systems. Each persona package models the public
  professional patterns of an exceptional builder, artist, researcher, or
  creative operator, with separate layers for raw research, machine-readable
  data, synthesized context modules, agent prompts, evaluation rubrics, and
  safety boundaries.
keywords:
  - persona
  - context-engineering
  - agents
  - llm
  - evidence-bound
  - non-impersonation
  - research-synthesis
license: MIT
version: 0.1.0
date-released: "2026-05-15"
